body.value:
Dear Administrator,
Please find the attached Status Report for EC to NGA PEX integration process execution. The attached file is of type CSV and the fields in it are pipe('|') delimited.

Hi,

Attached is the summary of employee extracted in Snapshot mode.

Thank?you.
